sequenceDiagram
    participant Kafka
    participant ASR as ASR Service (Controller)
    participant RayHead as Ray Cluster
    participant RayWorker as Ray Actor (Whisper Worker)

    Note over RayWorker: Init: Model Loaded in GPU VRAM (Warm)

    Kafka->>ASR: New Event: "Speech Segment A"
    
    %% Decision logic
    ASR->>ASR: Check Config: EXECUTION_MODE=ray
    
    %% Offloading
    ASR->>RayWorker: remote_call.transcribe(audio_bytes)
    activate RayWorker
    Note right of RayWorker: No model loading delay!<br/>Immediate Inference.
    RayWorker-->>ASR: return "Hello World"
    deactivate RayWorker

    ASR->>Kafka: Produce TextRecognizedEvent